Nitpicks: 



Webcrawler S29F87 () is to search online for keywords pertaining to SCP-5042-A bi-hourly, with all results forwarded to Site-28.
附加记录：    

The problem with using terms like  I suggest clarifying.



Upon verification, Mobile Task Force Mu-50 () is to be dispatched immediately, retrieve SCP-5042-A materials and locally disperse amnestics.
附加记录：    

This sentence feels a bit clanky. Also  of what?

